name: #2-3 Tiwa (The Four Fairies)
description:
This is a separate sub-collection of my Dream Dolls Collection. Nice to meet you "Tiwa".

Tiwa is a fairy of light. Her hair always had a golden glow. And the lines in your hair are hopes and successes that shine on me. Today's dreams are bright and full of hope, happiness and success. Thank you for today that you appeared to me.
